## 4. tools-config.json

**Location:** `/worksp/monitor/app/apps/nas-mcp/tools-config.json`

**Schema:**
```json
{
  "_readme": "...",
  "enabled_read_tools": ["check_system_info", "list_volumes", ...],
  "enabled_write_tools": ["restart_monitor_agent", "start_btrfs_scrub", ...]
}
```

**How it works:**
- Read at server startup (lines 50–58 of `index.ts`):
  ```typescript
  const toolsConfig = JSON.parse(readFileSync(configPath, "utf8")) as {
    enabled_read_tools: string[];
    enabled_write_tools: string[];
  };
  const enabledRead = new Set<string>(toolsConfig.enabled_read_tools ?? []);
  const enabledWrite = new Set<string>(toolsConfig.enabled_write_tools ?? []);
